description.en: IQC- Intelligence Quickly Chain is a public chain with large system frame capacity and strong bearing capacity. IQC is designed based on blockchain technology. The design core of the product and the main network is decentralized. Based on the agreed specifications and protocols, all nodes can safely verify and exchange data within the system without any artificial Intervene. IQC does not rely on third-party institutions or hardware facilities, there is no centralized control, and the technology itself is open source. The data is open to everyone, anyone can query the blockchain data and develop applications through the public interface.
